        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(C) In nomine domini Dei et Hominis. Anno incarnationis eiusdem millesimo
                        centesimo vigesimo secundo, mensis augusti, die secunda, indicione
                        quintadecima. Constat nos <persName ref="#people/3551"
                            key="#childOf #mundualdusOf #Lombard #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Villas #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Legumes #Wine #Forests #Rivers #Canals #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fisheries #Mills #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Venditio"
                            >Ugocionem</persName> de <placeName ref="#places/4107">Bahone</placeName>
                        et <persName ref="#people/3552"
                            key="#parentOf #Lombard #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Villas #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Legumes #Wine #Forests #Rivers #Canals #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fisheries #Mills #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Venditio"
                            >Helicam</persName>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">matrem</rs> et <rs key="#childOf">filium</rs>, ipso
                        filio ac <rs key="#mundualdusOf">mundoaldo</rs> meo mihi consentiente et
                        auctoritatem suam interponente, qui professi sumus nos lege vivere <rs
                            key="#Lombard">Longobardorum</rs>, accepisse a te domno <persName ref="#people/3550"
                            key="#Priors #Monasteries">Rodulpho</persName>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Priors #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Villas #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Legumes #Wine #Forests #Rivers #Canals #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fisheries #Mills #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Venditio"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2075">Sancti Cypriani</orgName> de <placeName
                            key="#Monasteries #Curtes" ref="#places/914">Venetia</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Priors">priore</rs>
                        <rs key="#Price">denariorum Venetialium libras centum</rs> finitum precium
                        sicut inter nos convenit, nominative pro omnibus rebus immobiliusf quę nobis
                            <rs key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">iure proprietatis</rs> pertinent
                        sive per hereditatem seu per qualemcumque acquisitionem in <geogName
                            ref="#estates/2072"
                            key="#Villas #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Legumes #Wine #Forests #Rivers #Canals #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fisheries #Mills #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                ><rs key="#Villas">villa</rs> scilicet quaei dicitur <placeName
                                ref="#places/4105" key="#Villas">Castellum de
                            Brenta</placeName></geogName> et in finibus ac territoriis eius, una cum
                            <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">sediminibus</rs> seu <rs key="#Cereals">terris
                            arabilibus</rs>, vigris, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Legumes">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Hay/fodder #Animals">pascuis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests">silvis
                            ac stellareis</rs>, <rs key="#Rivers">rivis</rs> ac <rs
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">paludibus</rs>, <rs key="#Mills"
                            >molendinis</rs>, <rs key="#Fisheries">piscationibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">venationibus</rs>, cultis
                        et incultis, divisis et indivisis, una cum finibus, terminibus et <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">usibus aquarum</rs>
                        <rs key="#Canals">aquarumque ductibus</rs>, cum omni iure ac iacentiis et
                        servitutibus earum rerum per loca et vocabula ad easdem res secundum usum et
                        consuetudinem prefatę villę in integrum. Quam autem venditionem superius
                        descriptam ab hac die tibi cui supra Rodulpho et per te mediantem tuo
                        monasterio quod est ad honorem Dei et Sancti Cypriani situm pro iam dicto
                        precio nos qui supra mater et filius, vendimus, tradimus et mancipamus,
                        nulli alii venditam, donatam, alienatam vel traditam nisi tibi et ecclesię
                        tuę ut facias exinde a presenti die tu et tuum monasterium iure ac nomine
                        proprietario quicquid volueritis, omni nostra et heredum nostrorum remota
                        contradictione. Quidem et spondemus atque promittimus nos et heredes nostros
                        tibi cui supra domno Rodulpho tuoque monasterio predictam venditionem
                        qualiter superius legitur in integrum ab omni homine defensare. Quod si
                        defendere non potuerimus aut si vobis exinde aliquid per quodvis ingenium
                        extorquere presumpserimus, tunc <rs key="#Penalty">in duplum</rs> eandem
                        venditionem ut prelegitur vobis restituemus sicut pro tempore fuerit
                        meliorata aut valuerit sub estimatione in consimilibus locis. Et ne nobis
                        liceat ullo tempore nolle quod voluimus id quod a nobis semel factum vel
                        conscriptum est inviolabiliter conservare promittimus cum stipulatione
                        sunbixa. Nichil enim nobis ex ipso precio deberi diximus. Actum in Venetia,
                        in <rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs>
                        <persName key="#Curtes #Witness #Venditio #parentOf"><name
                                ref="Dominicus/Barbi">Dominici Barbi</name></persName> feliciter.
                        Signa ++ manuum supradictorum Ugocionis et Helicę qui hanc <rs
                            key="#Venditio">cartulam venditionis</rs> fieri rogitarunt. Rogati autem
                        sunt <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>
                        <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"><name ref="Ardericus de Padua"
                                >Ardericus</name></persName>
                        <rs>legis doctus</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/41">Padua</placeName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"><name ref="Melius de Carraria"
                                >Melius</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/4106"
                            >Carraria</placeName>, de Venetia vero Dominicus Barbus et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Venditio #childOf"><name ref="Marcus"
                            >Marcus</name></persName> filius eius ac <persName
                            key="#Witness #Venditio "><name ref="Petrus/Zopulus">Petrus
                                Zopulus</name></persName>. (M) <persName
                            key="#Causidicus #Tabellio #Writer #Venditio"><name ref="Ionas"
                                >Ionas</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Causidicus">causidicus</rs> necnonque <rs key="#Tabellio"
                            >tabellio</rs> dictus huius contractus <rs key="#Writer">conscripsi</rs>
                        pacta rogatus. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
